    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a benchmark of atmospheric performance featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically superlative, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gate engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis is strictly dialed, retaining its factory-spec torsional rigidity with no evidence of fatigue. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero oxidation or road-rash, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the serious collector seeking a pure, analog driving experience.",
