    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as a time capsule. This car has been fastidiously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a single day of inclement weather. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating; the body is laser-straight, free of rock chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, retaining that distinct factory-fresh scent. The premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the high-gloss wood trim remains vibrant and scratch-free. Every technological feature, from the intuitive infotainment system to the precision climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the rigorous preventative maintenance schedule followed since day one. Included in the sale are all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual still in its plastic wrap, and a complete binder of service documentation. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to own a showroom-standard example that requires nothing but a driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
