      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless coachwork to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom delivery. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically pristine, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such distinguished caliber.",
